Report from the presentation of the Economic Award to the DRAMIŃSKI Company SA for the developed ultrasound scanner. The award is granted by the President of the Republic of Poland. It is a distinction for companies which make a significant contribution to the development of the economy, building a positive image of Polish entrepreneurship around the world.
